# Test Kubernetes Deployment

Create nginx deployment:

```bash
kubectl create deployment nginx --image=nginx
```

Expose deployment:

```bash
kubectl expose deployment nginx --type=NodePort --port=80
```

Check resources:

```bash
kubectl get all
```
